        <skos:prefLabel xml:lang="en">Waiting Room</skos:prefLabel>
        <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">A room provided for the use of people waiting for a service, such as a train or bus service, or to see an individual such as a doctor or a dentist. When a dedicated structure, see Thesaurus of Monument Types.</skos:scopeNote>
      </skos:Concept>
