        <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">A bladed wheel attached to the rear, and at right angles to the main sails, of a windmill.  Connected to winding gear, the fantail would catch the wind when it changed direction, allowing the mill to move automatically into the wind.</skos:scopeNote>
      </skos:Concept>
    </skos:narrower>

