        <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">The smallest piece of timber (2-5cms) across used in building, employed on rafters to support the roof covering or in a partition as a base for plaster or external render and wall covering.</skos:scopeNote>
      </skos:Concept>
    </skos:narrower>

