        <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">Series of rooms in a workhouse, prison or hospital, often including porter's lodge, baths, clothes store, washrooms, casual cells, rooms etc, for receiving inmates/patients. Use term in Monument Type Thesaurus if it is a freestanding building.</skos:scopeNote>
      </skos:Concept>
