        <skos:prefLabel xml:lang="en">Horse Engine</skos:prefLabel>
        <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">A device or engine powered by one or more horses or donkeys walking around a circular track and harnessed  so as to turn a large toothed wheel, either in the same plane or above, which turned smaller  wheels operating machinery.</skos:scopeNote>
      </skos:Concept>
    </skos:narrower>

