        <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">A machine for combing the fibres of cotton, worsted, flax etc to remove short fibres, clean out extraneous matter, and lay the fibres more or less parallel to each other.</skos:scopeNote>
      </skos:Concept>
    </skos:narrower>

